{"tid":2217082,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"照片裡是誰？　IZ*ONE答案令全場震驚⋯網衝擊：時代差異？","createTime":"2020-09-25T07:35:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T15:14:57.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"64f4965c64050e46798fc4fe51f865dc4b6a57a9","tid":2217082,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T07:35:15.000Z","msg":"南韓人氣綜藝《新西遊記》熱門遊戲環節「人物問答」，主持人需在極短的時間內要反應答出照片裡的人物，對此，藝人多次出現爆笑的錯誤答案，「笑」果連連，深受觀眾喜愛。近來，女團IZ*ONE也在個人真人秀裡玩起該遊戲，好萊塢男神李奧納多狄卡皮歐（Leonardo DiCaprio）照片出現時，成員卻一時愣住沒答出來，令許多網友震驚直呼「這是時代差異嗎」、「居然沒認出來」，在網路上引起陣陣討論。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5163/d5163893.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5163%2Fd5163893.jpg&h=e7dfb817&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼玟周沒有認出影帝真面目。（圖／翻攝自Mnet）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5163/d5163894.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5163%2Fd5163894.jpg&h=ed1ab10e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIZ*ONE近日推出最新團綜《 IZONE CHU：ON:TACT》，製作單位擺出一桌美食，條件是她們必須闖關成功，其中一個環節，她們得答出節目公開的公眾人物照片，起初劉在錫、姜虎東等人的照片都對答如流，但突然出現一位好萊塢演員李奧納多狄卡皮歐，玟周一時沒認出影帝真面目，奈子更秒答「那不是狄卡皮歐」，兩人沒有認出影帝李奧納多，令不少網友直呼「天阿怎麼會不知道」、「14歲小孩都知道吧」、「衝擊」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5163/d5163895.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5163%2Fd5163895.jpg&h=21b0b190&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲奈子搶答表示「那不是狄卡皮歐」，反應令網友衝擊不已。（圖／翻攝自Mnet）<br />\n<br />\n不僅如此，IZ*ONE爾後又再度答錯南韓足球選手朴智星，這2個片段引起正、反面意見熱烈討論，不少人認為她們太無知，但也有粉絲為她們緩頰可能是太緊張了，也有人試著舒緩氣氛表示「因為是玟周可以原諒」。<br />\n<br />\n周周我女友。。。"},{"pid":"150aba1daed3a5b2911c264a7a1767223649be02","tid":2217082,"uid":46435,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T07:38:19.000Z","msg":"奈子真係傻妹黎 連萊昂納多迪卡普里奧都唔識真係要話下佢先得.."},{"pid":"77f3452efb6b83e70cc8e8f55b970fcad9a656f4","tid":2217082,"uid":184233,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T07:39:49.000Z","msg":"對家都認唔出IZONE一樣"},{"pid":"0415c58e0dc2156df563060c4533d38a081e6337","tid":2217082,"uid":152432,"like":11,"dislike":5,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"77f3452efb6b83e70cc8e8f55b970fcad9a656f4","tid":2217082,"uid":184233,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T07:39:49.000Z","msg":"對家都認唔出IZONE一樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T07:42:27.000Z","msg":"IZone堆女人選秀節目求其都一大堆，砌到10隊Izone都得<br />\n但係冇人取代到Leonardo<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0a9f12b2b5174a04cd988abce9a1c6a1b618b17","tid":2217082,"uid":190258,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T07:50:55.000Z","msg":"新西遊記都成日會答錯啦 好撚出奇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e09275d64c961b51ea4395e934cec90fc6527b5c","tid":2217082,"uid":15371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T13:34:59.000Z","msg":"劇本黎<br />\n<br />\n利申我係寫手"},{"pid":"f064c4b0841bdc95e56bfc81119d1b674ccb2367","tid":2217082,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T13:35:46.000Z","msg":"Nako成日對住佢黎打碟"},{"pid":"ca4cd184024e0461c3afc99e572f862a5d093665","tid":2217082,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T13:40:52.000Z","msg":"鬼佬個個差唔多樣點認呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f08c92489c223369a2f488c753c9a66a0af875d9","tid":2217082,"uid":68678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:24:20.000Z","msg":"無知妹妹無咁上下"},{"pid":"0bf003b566de352f65389155608ec739679e3a6f","tid":2217082,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:59:09.000Z","msg":"周周傻更更咁qq到&hellip;"},{"pid":"e6e5d92d003199f88e003a7410cfdc82ca0f2661","tid":2217082,"uid":374048,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T15:14:57.000Z","msg":"其實佢哋細個開始練習,都冇機會見識其他嘢,唔識有乜出奇??<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcr